'''阿图岛'''（{{lang-en|Attu}}、{{lang-ale|Atan}}）是[[美国|美国]][[阿拉斯加州|阿拉斯加州]][[阿留申群岛|阿留申群岛]]中最西端的一个岛屿，目前无人居住。<ref name="publicbroadcasting.net">{{cite news|url=http://kucb.org/news/article/alaska-coast-guard-says-goodbye-to-its-last-loran-station/|title=Alaska Coast Guard says goodbye to its last LORAN station|publisher=Unalaska Community Broadcasting|work=KUCB News|date=August 27, 2010|accessdate=August 28, 2010|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181119015042/http://www.kucb.org/news/article/alaska-coast-guard-says-goodbye-to-its-last-loran-station|archive-date=2018-11-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>在[[第二次世界大战|第二次世界大战]]中，该岛曾一度被[[日本|日本]]占领，称为热田岛。1943年5月，美军为夺回阿图岛在这里[[阿圖島戰役|与日军展开激战]]，结果岛上日军被几乎全歼。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://tv.cntv.cn/video/C14107/dc9852e45bee3ddd9a91f6da0a4e5c44 |title=《档案》 20130402 1943美军血战冰原收复阿图岛 |access-date=2017-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170904065120/http://tv.cntv.cn/video/C14107/dc9852e45bee3ddd9a91f6da0a4e5c44 |archive-date=2017-09-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=阿图岛争夺战:2战美唯一国土沦陷|url=http://war.163.com/12/0529/11/82LTS8PO0001123L.html|accessdate=2017-09-03|agency=上海新民晚报|publisher=网易新闻|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170904063857/http://war.163.com/12/0529/11/82LTS8PO0001123L.html|archive-date=2017-09-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=二战美国有两处荒岛被日军占领，美军不惜死伤两千的代价也要夺回|url=http://wemedia.ifeng.com/20314507/wemedia.shtml|website=凤凰号|accessdate=2017-09-03|archive-date=2020-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021043930/http://wemedia.ifeng.com/20314507/wemedia.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

